import React from "react"; import { Col, Container, Row } from "react-bootstrap"; const About = () => { return (
About me
Hello, I'm Shubham Chikhale, a recent graduate in Computer Science and Engineering with a keen interest in Front-end Development and React. I have completed several online courses and have hands-on experience in creating web applications using React. I'm excited about the latest front-end development trends and enjoy working with modern web technologies. I'm always eager to learn and try new things in the field of front-end development. I have developed a few web applications using React, HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript. I'm familiar with Git and have experience in collaborating with other developers using GitHub. Apart from technical skills, I also have excellent communication and teamwork skills, which I have developed through various team projects and internships. I believe that these skills, combined with my technical knowledge, make me an ideal candidate for any front-end React developer position. In my free time, I like to explore new technologies and contribute to open-source projects. I'm also interested in attending tech conferences and meetups to learn from other developers and network with like-minded individuals. If you're interested in working with me or have any questions, please feel free to contact me at shubham.chikhale@example.com or connect with me on LinkedIn. I would love to hear from you!
); }; export default About;
